## Project

B2B landing page for Яндекс Путешествия (Yandex Travel for Business).
Single-page site: `index.html` + `assets/` folder. No frameworks, no bundler.

## Code style

- HTML: semantic tags, BEM class naming
- CSS: one file per section in `assets/styles/`, BEM methodology
- JS: vanilla ES5+ in `assets/scripts/`, no modules
- All asset paths relative: `assets/…`
- Keep Russian content, `lang="ru"`, `charset="UTF-8"`

## Git commands

Push all changes:
```sh
git add -A && git commit -m "your message" && git push origin main
```

Push specific files:
```sh
git add <files> && git commit -m "your message" && git push origin main
```
